  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK750">
<l>eṉaimāṭcit tākiyak kaṇṇum viṉaimāṭci</l>
<l>yillārka ṇillai yaraṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although a fort may possess all (the above-said) excellence, it is, as it were without these, if its inmates possess not the excellence of action.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
